# PyTetris

An implementation of Tetris with [textual.textualize.io](https://textual.textualize.io/) library.
The game is played in a terminal.

## Controls

```
a - move left
d - move right
w - rotate counter clockwise
s - rotate clockwise
l - move down
space - restart the game after the game is over
Ctrl+C - exit
```
